summary: Now that the year is coming to the end, I’ve decided to share with y’all my favorite pages from my first bullet journal. It’s...
body:
Now that the year is coming to the end, I’ve decided to share with y’all my favorite pages from my first bullet journal. It’s been an incredible and happy and painful journey, I’ve learned a lot about myself this year and will continue to do so by loving myself (you can’t stop me lovin’ myself~ lol)

If you’re starting a bullet journal just remember to have fun, be creative, it doesn’t have to be aesthetically pleasing, just be you. I had lots of fun with the themed ones. Like series, art, music, you can even write song lyrics. I also wrote BTS’ United Nations speech cause they inspire me so much and I’m so grateful to have them in my life. And y’all remember Outcast, that shit was fireee~

Can’t wait for 2019, focus on yourself, block them negative people in your lives and have a Happy (early) new year!!!

summary: Hey there! I'd like to have a ship please if that's cool! I'm 5'3", 26 but look like 16. positive, goal driven, hates ppl until...
question: Hey there! I'd like to have a ship please if that's cool! I'm 5'3", 26 but look like 16. positive, goal driven, hates ppl until convinced otherwise. huge circle of friends, the shoulder to lean on and lives and breathes music. loves games, sports, languages, traveling, photography and coffee. I go from social butterfly to grumpy hermit in 0,00001 seconds. sassy and can be kind of an asshole too. also honest to the bone, ye.
answer:
Of course :)

I ship you with Jin ! He’s such a chill guy and so nice and fun that he won’t be hurt if you’re not very nice to him while in a bad mood ad he’ll also respect when you need your alone time and no one bothering you. He’d love to do all the things you love with you, traveling, games and he’ll of course make you take pictures of him everywhere but he’d also take thousands of you so he can brag about you to the world. You’d definitely not be bored with him and can count on him as well.

Just a very chill relationship, enjoying each others compagnie. Kind of like dating your best friend.
